        "rich_text_6DiAmh": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing a gift is never easy, especially for the woman you love. It is not just about what you’re gifting but why are you gifting it - the though and the emotion behind it. Unlike flowers that wilt and chocolates that disappear, jewelry stays, a memory captured in gold and a promise etched on stone. You don’t want to show up with the bare minimum gestures when it comes to showering love on your partner, who supports you, grows with you, and inspires you. So, we curated a list of 10 romantic jewelry gift ideas for your girlfriend for every phase of your relationship.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ik4Knd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Playful Spark - Diamond Bow Stud Earrings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Playful Spark - Diamond Bow Stud Earrings</h2>",
            "custom_id": "spark",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_w33dwC": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Every relationship begins with a spark - those late night conversations, those stealing glances, the excitement of meeting each other, the warmness in your heart when you confide in each other. Love feels playful and effortless, the little gestures mean the world - walking her home, opening the door, remembering how she likes her coffee and choosing a thoughtful gift can be difficult. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "3-00-ct-elegant-princess-cut-diamond-stud-earrings",
              "3-prong-set-round-diamond-solitaire-stud-earrings"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_igLJQq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>These diamond bow <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a> are the most versatile diamond studs for such beginnings! These earrings become more than an accessory, they become the keepsake of your first chapter of love. These sparkling stud earrings symbolize the beginnings of such beautiful stories - subtle enough for everyday wear and timelessly special enough for her to treasure forever. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UQ3KpC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Blooming Phase - Petal Bloom Diamond Pendant",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Blooming Phase - Petal Bloom Diamond Pendant</h2>",
            "custom_id": "blooming",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wrjzp4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_dca94e00-4536-462a-9eb2-51352c46da87.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Put an end to the doubt - ‘he loves me, he loves me not.’ Floral designs in jewelry date back centuries, first started in the Victorian era to symbolize romance. Just as love unfolds petal by petal, and blooms into something that just becomes sweeter with passing time, this petal bloom diamond pendant is a symbol of everlasting love. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "bloom-cluster-diamond-pendant",
              "bezel-set-round-diamond-pendant"
            ]
          }
        },
