          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/pendant-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Pendant Necklace\">pendant necklace</a> is a piece that wonderfully transitions from casual coffee dates to evening dinners. A luxurious design that is crafted with precision and diamonds that sparkle for a lifetime, this necklace gift for girlfriend reflects how you feel for her. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
