            "text": "<p>If you are looking for a modern design that goes with every look, and walks with her to every room, this Radiance Trio Diamond Pendant is what you are looking for. With three stunning diamond perfectly set to create a design so subtly royal, this diamond pendant necklace will make her eyes shine and awe every time she looks at it. </p>",
