        "rich_text_wpFtdV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>After all, receiving a diamond ring is a woman’s dream come true. If you are ready to pop the big question and are looking for an <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Engagement Ring\">engagement ring</a>, you can also customize a 1 carat diamond ring. </p>",
